Achievements.Title: Wright Brothers True Master Pilot Award
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Expert without ever losing a wing
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Rogue Fox
Achievements.Description: Clear the game on Expert without wingmen completing any stage
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: CCCC (200 Corneria City)
Achievements.Description: Break 200 hits on Corneria and complete the stage
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: 4x4
Achievements.Description: In Metos get four plus4 combos in a row (hint R and Z prevents lock on)
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Untouchable
Achievements.Description: Complete Sector Y on expert without taking damage
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Blaster Master (Sector Y)
Achievements.Description: Get 120 hits before the boss using charged shot and bombs (no laser)
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: ID4 Finish on Katina
Achievements.Description: Destroy the mothership core with less that 3 seconds on the clock
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Clam on a halfshell
Achievements.Description: Destroy Bio-Weapon, killing barnicles, with left and right side down as it dies
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Silverless Solar Survival
Achievements.Description: Finish Solar. Don't get any s. rings or let your life empty (star, g. rings ok)
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Solar Daredevil 8000
Achievements.Description: Survive most of the stage above 7800 degrees  - vid guide available on game page
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Arwing action
Achievements.Description: Play through Zoness in Cockpit view
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Lone Defender Sector Z
Achievements.Description: Destroy all the missiles and complete the mission without any allies around
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: In charge without charge
Achievements.Description: Get 280 kills in Area 06 Expert without using the charged laser or bombs
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Arwing Item Hunter
Achievements.Description: Collect 19 items in Area 6 ~(5 rings, 4 bombs, 6 gold rings, 6 lasers)
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Venom Flyby
Achievements.Description: Reach the temple in Expert without killing an enemy
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Ancient Robot Chase (Venom I)
Achievements.Description: Destroy Golemech before 66 on the leaderboard. Hint- listen to Falco
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Achievements.Title: Outgunned (Venom II)
Achievements.Description: Defeat all 4 Starwolf using single laser and getting plus50 combos from each
Achievements.Author: kdecks

Leaderboards.Title: Venom I Golemech
Leaderboards.Description: Race! How quickly (in distance) can you beat Golemech?
